e simple reason that he found anti-McCarthyists much more repulsive than McCarthy himself. Since, moreover, it does not reflect any statement occuring in PNIN, this sentence on the jacket, says VN, is absurd and must be removed.

When both above-mentioned matters have been taken care of please send us a sample copy. May we please hear from you by return mail?





Yours truly,

(Mrs. Vladimir Nabokov)





